Listen everyone, I've been having computer and social problems and 
that's why I haven't been posting like I promised. And I think I've 
fallen too far behind in the story, and it wouldn't be fair to take 
back my chars. So, Yanshosh already has Fliq and Logo already has 
Starscream and Vulois. You guys can keep them, if it's all right with 
you. Now, Soulstice and I were disscussing something that I could do 
with Fliq and one of his chars, but Fliq is already with Yanshosh. So 
I'm giving Gotron to Soulstice, and he can use him as he wants. But 
that still leaves The Trainers and Savage up in the air. If you want 
them, e-mail me. I'm not sure I want to give possesion of all of them 
to one person. I would be too much power. I may even keep one of them 
just to make sure everything doesn't go out of control. But e-mail if 
you want them. Tomorrow at about this time I will have my new chars 
up. I have it all set out and everything, but I'm try to work out 
kinks in the origin stories. So, I'll see you all tomorrow. And thank 
you all for being patient with me. It means a lot to me.
